    <mxCell id="queue" value="&lt;b&gt;SCHEDULER LOGIC — PRIORITY ONLY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Jobs are ordered and dispatched based solely on:&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;1.  Priority class (High → Medium → Low)&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;2.  Submission time (first-in, first-out within same priority)&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;3.  Resource fit (can the job fit on the next available node block?)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font color=&#39;#b85450&#39;&gt;✘  No awareness of what time of day it is&lt;br/&gt;✘  No awareness of the current or forecast grid carbon intensity&lt;br/&gt;✘  No distinction made between time-critical and delay-tolerant jobs&lt;br/&gt;✘  Every job is treated as if it must run immediately&lt;/font&gt;"
