    <mxCell id="grid" value="&lt;b&gt;TENNESSEE VALLEY AUTHORITY (TVA) — ELECTRICITY GRID&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;The grid dispatches whatever fuel mix is needed to meet current demand.&lt;br/&gt;The data centre has zero visibility and zero influence over this mix.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mean generation mix (2019–2022, source: EIA API):&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Nuclear (NUC)   ████████████████░░░░░░░░  41%  →     0 gCO₂/kWh&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Natural Gas (NG) ███████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  28%  →   450 gCO₂/kWh&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Coal (COL)       ███████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  18%  → 1,000 gCO₂/kWh&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Hydro (WAT)      █████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  13%  →     0 gCO₂/kWh&lt;br/&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Solar (SUN)      ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░  &lt;1%  →     0 gCO₂/kWh&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mean carbon intensity: 283 gCO₂/kWh  |  Hourly range: 76 – 500 gCO₂/kWh&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font color=&#39;#b85450&#39;&gt;✘  Carbon intensity changes every hour — this information is never queried&lt;br/&gt;✘  The scheduler has no connection to grid data of any kind&lt;br/&gt;✘  Missed opportunity: intensity can vary by up to 2× within a single day&lt;/font&gt;"
      style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingRight=12;spacingTop=8;fontSize=12;verticalAlign=top;"
      vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="80" y="1078" width="1100" height="290" as="geometry"/>
