    <mxCell id="nodes" value="&lt;b&gt;COMPUTING NODES — 4,626 Nodes (ORNL Summit / In-Premise Data Centre)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;• Idle nodes consume:   ~350–400W standby (unavoidable baseline draw)&lt;br/&gt;• Active nodes (job running):   700–900W drawn from the grid via PSU inputs&lt;br/&gt;• Power draw is measured by hardware sensors (BMC + NVIDIA DCGM) but never reported back to the scheduler&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font color=&#39;#b85450&#39;&gt;✘  No carbon cost is recorded per job execution&lt;br/&gt;✘  No signal sent back to the scheduler about energy consumption&lt;br/&gt;✘  No awareness of whether a greener window exists in the next 48 hours&lt;/font&gt;"
      style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingRight=12;spacingTop=8;fontSize=12;verticalAlign=top;"
