    <mxCell id="reporting" value="&lt;b&gt;Operations Manager&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;✔  Knows: job runtime, queue wait time, node utilisation rate&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font color=&#39;#b85450&#39;&gt;✘  Does not know: carbon cost per job, grid CI at time of execution&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Sustainability / Compliance Officer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;font color=&#39;#b85450&#39;&gt;✘  Cannot report Scope 2 emissions at job or hourly level&lt;br/&gt;✘  Relies only on annual electricity bills — no hourly carbon breakdown&lt;br/&gt;✘  Cannot produce an EU CSRD-compliant audit trail&lt;br/&gt;✘  Cannot demonstrate emission reduction targets or track progress toward them&lt;/font&gt;"
      style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;align=left;spacingLeft=14;spacingRight=12;spacingTop=8;fontSize=12;verticalAlign=top;"
